commitResults.messageTitle: [Level-1] Updated Felix(Duke) to echo commands entered by the user and exit when user types bye.
[Level-2] Add ability to store text and display them using an array.

[Level-3] Mark as done: Added the ability to mark tasks as done and undone. Additionally, added the tasklist class to hold the list of all tasks. Abstracted out the relevant functionality to the tasklist and task class accordingly.
[Level-4] Added ToDo, Deadlines and Events subclasses. 1. Updated Duke, Task and TaskList accordingly so that all functionalities work with new subclasses 2. Updated toString methods
[A-TextUiTesting] Performed some UI tests using I/O redirection 1. Tested default greeting by chatbot 2. Tested creation of todos and deadlines
[Level-5] Handled some relevant errors, null pointer, index out of bounds, number format and illegal argument.

[Level-6] Added a delete function. - Changed the data structure used from a primitive array to arraylist. - Modified the relevant functions in tasklist accordingly. - Edited duke to accomodate for new function and added exception handling for it.
Added Javadocs to document all of the code.
